# No API key required — this agent uses Ollama (local AI, runs on your PC).
#
# Setup:
#   1. Install Ollama: https://ollama.com/download
#   2. Run: ollama pull qwen2.5-coder:7b
#   3. Ollama starts automatically on boot — nothing else needed.
#
# To change the model, edit MODEL in ai_test_agent.py
